Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.91,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.58,0:00:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.12,0:00:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.23,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.44,0:00:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.24,0:00:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.52,0:01:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民衛星派來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五部鋼彈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.58,0:01:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是衛星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈藏身在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.46,0:01:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合軍的機動戰士部隊內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以OZ為攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開了各種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ終於踏上歷史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,統帥特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.48,0:01:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以精銳的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行了消滅聯合軍的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派來地球的機動戰士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的戰鬥令大地震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛先生啊，拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功率10%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他會做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恥的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的…錯誤!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九話\N[亡國的肖像]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你這個[閃光男爵]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.51,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美麗的城市才沒受到戰火蹂躪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.18,0:02:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被攻其不備後，聯合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.58,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘餘軍力也在重整陣形吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡就用作今後的戰鬥總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城市的美貌\N誰來支配也不會變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，OZ的目的不是支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從聯合勢力裡解放各國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的目的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由隸屬OZ的我來說也許很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向犯了建立聯合\N這個錯誤的各國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次給予考慮機會的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以得到其應有的評價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從維多利亞基地來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士運輸機到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧圖!我在等你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在報到，傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才叫你別勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧圖特尉現在根本不能站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肋骨斷了，內臟也受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你期待已久的托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是匹相當難馴服的悍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是託爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來一點都不像20年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製作途中放棄的實驗作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，噴射器產生的迴轉速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定是艾亞利玆的3倍以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但最高速度卻計算不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我在中途失去知覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是測試駕駛員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯不是其他人能駕御的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了傑克斯特尉之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太過獎我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我相信你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，讓我馬上使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你勉強駕駛真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶奧圖特尉去醫務室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，叫機動戰士部隊\N準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊地球圈統一聯合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從聯合手裡解放她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳對這任務沒不滿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛這部托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上在實戰使用它!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我想用這部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試我的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國，傑克斯的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進得好，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回應她們啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得她們來打氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊轉校一邊移動\N是個好辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這年紀上學是自然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算裝成普通人一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太張揚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為，自然地行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比躲躲藏藏藏較不會令人起疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也盡情享受\N正常的學校生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別連累我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還要說[別妨礙我]吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我的目標也和你一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想瞞我也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.42,0:06:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼內清楚映著那要塞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來比快好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到你了，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想見要殺死自己的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位小姐真古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現大量機動戰士\N用大型運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正接近本基地!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是OZ的部隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的傢伙在打甚麼主意!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士出擊了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別散開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能佔領中樞設施就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於OZ的政變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈統一聯合變得非常混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各地的基地，聯合的軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不能了解實際情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了解決各國之間的糾紛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而建立的地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,異常地擴張軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至以軍國主義壓制各國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣子被統一的很多國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.81,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ正在解放她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，聯合的軍力擴張問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的機動戰士部隊引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有很多國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對OZ這次行動存疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們認為仍以\N軍事力量支配各國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是聯合和OZ的名字對換罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士，全體出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請交由我掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你只想著達到目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已心無雜念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會引開地面部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我相信會有數部飛上空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據資料\N我能加速甩掉他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以噴射器的馬力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,補救笨重機體的機動性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真荒謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不可輕視嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能在山克王國面前丟臉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔領東面的跑道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這加速足以殺人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高馬力就能甩掉敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?我為何猶疑不決?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ來的通訊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即解除武裝投降!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不想再和你們戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你們挑起戰端的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要投降的是你們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有光線砲準備發射!   遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光線砲!?\N是總部沒資料的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體迴避!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.98,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,區區光線砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵!命令全體離開這空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道他們\N有這麼厲害的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我還能作戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在暫時撤退重整陣形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後退到運輸機降落的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我變得很膽小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這部托爾吉斯做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把光線砲和司令部一起消滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕御過多種機動戰士的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?我怕甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有這部機動戰士的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何敵人也能打倒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，它有弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是駕駛員\N是血肉之驅的人類!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，一起喝好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.76,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次攻擊哪裡好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戰鬥吧，打贏就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.47,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣就能稱霸地球圈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.04,0:11:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠，那麼世人就會憎恨OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是成為世界的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被憎恨的人不可以不自強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對OZ來說也是好的鼓勵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一你有甚麼不測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們怎向衛星裡的老爺交代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們那麼不可靠嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不是那意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的存在是為了保護你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…拉席得隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不會再單獨行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我答應你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，沒時間呆著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不去整備機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你啊，拉席得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在生氣啊，請你不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括我，總共有5部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部的名字或許都是鋼彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部是鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.02,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們有點急躁冒失，但都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼知道他們是好人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙之心告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙之心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.41,0:13:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個一言不發好玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.52,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已過了兩小時啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太沒意思了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.02,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我想你們肚子餓拿來食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請趁熱吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放在這裡\N你們要全部吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，麻煩你們收拾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.53,0:14:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要從小學習修養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.84,0:14:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寡言的人比較會認識到寡言的朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許不太不好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本沒資格駕駛[哪吒]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脈搏大致上穩定下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，循環系統就很有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.38,0:14:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說我竟然能生還嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，究竟發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我輕視了那部托爾吉斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它完全不顧及駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.13,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它和正統的近代武器完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的設計是瘋狂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不顧及駕駛員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有想得出的戰鬥形式上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它被賜予了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.11,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僅一部機體也能完全取勝的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我變得膽小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我越想發揮那部\N機動戰士的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越是將自己逼到極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的力量到此為止了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不是戰鬥用機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是決鬥用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當駕駛員有不怕死的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能發揮它的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕死精神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使死也要勝利的精神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐懼竟然傷了自身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也還未成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，再次進攻山克王國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換成是普通人已經死了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去，請你在這裡等我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不駕駛\N托爾吉斯我就批準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.43,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們需要托爾吉斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的設計者應該和鋼彈的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如我以前所講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯是\N所有機動戰士的原型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的荒謬設計由鋼彈繼承了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我一定要成功駕御它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯\N原來是敢死攻擊用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣也就能理解鋼彈的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在找尋值得一死的戰場!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國在面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能袖手旁觀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在你要聽我說話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天傍晚出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯出發了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做甚麼? 馬上回來!奧圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這部托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能鎮壓山克王國的中樞設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我很清楚托爾吉斯的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止!你會死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果為了傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我死也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你也讓我協助你達到夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是為了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.39,0:17:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想為你效勞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧圖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以性命換來勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧圖!你在說甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來!奧圖!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我追著男孩來到這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你驚奇嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我無論如何想見希洛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心情爸爸你明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心底的創傷痊癒之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有希洛支持我不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他總是逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我搶先一步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經留下你的份囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!甚麼也看不見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別阻礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我不能支持那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我能駕御托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機動戰士正急速接近!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有光線砲集中攻擊那部機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯國王萬歲!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧圖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用了13年時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才再次踏上這片土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你原諒我父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，很多人因此流盡鮮血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能過著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違背你完全和平主義\N的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手被血染得太污穢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.47,0:21:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的我不能\N繼承匹斯克拉福特王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，她應該一定能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立父王你理想中的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會為了那目標而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你原諒我這個不肖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到攻擊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是衛星所為的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.94,0:21:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.17,0:21:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晨，小姐\N今日天氣也很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，我們要上課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.58,0:22:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我和你多在一起一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能變得和你一樣堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.61,0:22:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.61,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.61,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.11,0:23:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.61,0:23:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命的戰鬥只是錯誤的計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.14,0:23:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，奧圖的死意味著甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安提議把宇宙用機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯運去西伯利亞基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.09,0:23:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那原來是\N消滅鋼彈的誘敵之計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.39,0:23:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛在和傑克斯的決鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.19,0:23:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作出最後的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記鋼彈W   第十話
